Saratoga County confirmed two new #COVID19 linked deaths, a 57 y/o Clifton Park man & a 51 y/o Milton man.
As of April 20, 111,856 Saratoga County residents have received at least 1 dose of the #COVID19 #vaccine. 81,317 Saratoga County residents have completed the vaccine series. https://t.co/RVg45dOYEc
